==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsay
<hw>Un*say</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>say</ets>.]</ety> <def>To recant or recall, as
what has been said; to refract; to take back again; to make as if not
said.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>You can say and <qex>unsay</qex> things at pleasure.</q>
<rj><qau>Goldsmith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unscale</ent>⟦br⟧
